15:43.975 --> 15:46.376
Okay. Love you. Thank you.

15:46.377 --> 15:47.978
(chuckling):
Oh, my God.

15:47.979 --> 15:49.380
- Nice.
- Well done.

15:49.383 --> 15:51.048
