Everything okay back there?

16:11.669 --> 16:13.070
We're fine.
We're fine.

16:13.071 --> 16:14.872
Open the door and let her out.

16:14.873 --> 16:16.306
Open the freaking door
and let her out.

16:16.307 --> 16:17.808
I'm gonna actually drive there.

16:17.809 --> 16:19.910
PILOT:
Should we head back?

16:19.911 --> 16:21.378
MACY: You know
what would be really nice?

16:21.379 --> 16:23.480
