Wait, Macy. Seriously?

16:26.351 --> 16:28.352
SUNNY: Mace, honey,
honey, come on.

16:28.353 --> 16:30.021
- SAM: Oh, are you okay?
- Yeah.

16:30.024 --> 16:31.823
- Don't hit your head.
- I'll see you there.

16:31.826 --> 16:34.025
