MARK:
Welcome!

17:22.406 --> 17:26.543
Welcome, welcome.
The long wait is over!

17:26.544 --> 17:28.079
- My sunshine.
- Hi. Okay, um...

17:28.082 --> 17:29.913
(both moaning)

17:29.914 --> 17:31.182
MARK: Wow. That was worth it.

17:31.183 --> 17:32.449
(Sunny giggles)

17:32.450 --> 17:34.084
Mm. (kisses)

17:34.085 --> 17:35.886
- I love it.
