17:35.889 --> 17:37.320
Sounds so good.

17:37.321 --> 17:38.823
- SUNNY: You're hilarious.
- Yes.

17:38.826 --> 17:40.157
- Of course I am.
- MARK: Oh, that's funny.

17:40.160 --> 17:41.492
